# .secret-patterns — Farm-specific terms to block from commits
#
# Copy this file to .secret-patterns and add your own terms.
# This file is gitignored — each contributor maintains their own.
# One regex pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Examples:
# MyFarmName
# 123 Main Street
# my\.email@example\.com
# MyFarmDomain\.com
